QuestData.Title: Need More Teeth
QuestData.Description: <Prowler Sasha silently holds out his hand to reveal a necklace crafted of stained leather and putrid brown ogre teeth. All have a matching tone of rot to them.>$b$b<It has several knots that appear to be missing additional teeth.>
QuestData.RewardText: <Prowler Sasha nods and assembles two necklaces.>
